    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just don't see the point in filling the void. everything feels so heavy, like i'm just dragging myself through a life that doesn't even belong to me anymore. it's just constant exhaustion. do you think people are actually meant to carry this much pain? it feels like too much.",
